remixlab.bias.branch

Class GenericGrabberObject<E extends Enum<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • remixlab.bias.branch.GenericGrabberObject<E>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericGrabber<E>, Grabber

    public abstract class GenericGrabberObject<E extends Enum<E>>
extends Object
implements GenericGrabber<E>
    Default implementation of the GenericGrabber interface which eases implementation.

    Based on the concrete event type, this interactive grabber object splits the checkIfGrabsInput(BogusEvent) and the performInteraction(BogusEvent) methods into more specific versions of them, e.g., checkIfGrabsInput(ClickEvent), checkIfGrabsInput(DOF3Event), performInteraction(DOF6Event), performInteraction(KeyboardEvent) and so on. Thus allowing implementations of this abstract interactive grabber object to override only those method signatures that might be of their interest.

    This interactive grabber object implementation also provided an algorithm to parse an Action sequence from an init action variable, see processEvent(BogusEvent).
